{"tid":1849762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(特權) 黑警安排警車接親友拜年 長髮女車內打卡po微信被揭發","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:23:28.000Z","uid":222970,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e940c6c3a6f90fb1dd4cda804be21f38e9efd3d1","tid":1849762,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2BgTtu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2BgTtu.jpg&h=a8496247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhwD6OT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhwD6OT.jpg&h=11295102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9zNZ8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9zNZ8P.jpg&h=7bca2d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzmdbfv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuzmdbfv.jpg&h=7d7d4f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女事主在微信帳戶上載多張圖片，圖文並茂講述自己乘坐警車離開。<br />\n<br />\n過去7個多月警員紀律操守備受批評，農曆年期間更疑爆警員「公器私用」，用警車接載拜年親友「遊車河」醜聞。有網民近日在通訊軟件「微信」發現，一名疑為警務人員女親友人士，於個人賬戶上載多張圖片，圖文並茂講述年初二（26日）到紀律部隊宿舍拜年經歷。事主最後更疑獲安排乘坐警車離開，在帖文炫耀稱「最後係坐警車，人一世物一世，要坐下」，並上載一幅與男友在警車內的合照。據了解，警方未有因應農曆年，容許警員親友參觀警方車輛的安排，懷疑有人違紀。警方回覆《蘋果》查詢時稱，會了解事件，不容許警務人員作出違法或違紀行為。<br />\n有網民從微信軟件，留意到涉事帖文。該賬號名為「筠筠」女士，疑為警員親友。事主在帖文聲稱，今年農曆初二，曾到訪男友位於疑為紀律部隊宿舍的家中「派利是」，並上載圖片顯示宿舍大堂的牆身，貼有小童繪畫支持警察的畫作，事主形容「很有愛呀」。事主在帖文亦圖文並茂，介紹自己獲安排「坐警車」，並附上事主自己與男友在警車內的自拍合照，又展示兩張從警車內，向外拍攝街道情況的圖片。<br />\n警方發言人指會了解事件，強調非常重視人員的操守，不容許警務人員作出違法或違紀的行為。如有個別警務人員涉嫌違法或違紀，警方會按既定機制公平公正調查及積極跟進。"},{"pid":"65a611e84f54ed2b39af44266962d564db75a182","tid":1849762,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0469448a49cbcb7dd3bd6d0f90f6ef0189181e2c","tid":1849762,"uid":45910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"「一場誤會，沒事兒」"},{"pid":"42de5dd5804c14b473297f4958ede3c455268c7c","tid":1849762,"uid":184827,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:19:03.000Z","msg":"警方發言人指會了解事件，強調非常重視人員的操守，不容許警務人員作出違法或違紀的行為。如有個別警務人員涉嫌違法或違紀，警方會按既定機制公平公正調查及積極跟進。<br />\n<br />\n世紀大笑話"},{"pid":"62e74a9bd21e3c2f4ec8ed250eb5f44b36c2c521","tid":1849762,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=8462a058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度簽得七七八八<br />\n麻煩fb tg發出去搵新客源簽"},{"pid":"f8d9cbf2c4eb566bff6da3e39668e358cc4a1546","tid":1849762,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjrMrcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjrMrcp.jpg&h=e20e71f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n組織工會 全面罷工</span></span><br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"903fdf528422444644b013e8f5fd41e4afaf0543","tid":1849762,"uid":219767,"l